00:26:01.840 --> 00:26:05.640
that let them be killed and be born again

00:26:05.880 --> 00:26:09.280
because they're so impure but Christ had hopes

00:26:09.400 --> 00:26:11.720
that He can transform people,

00:26:11.840 --> 00:26:16.600
but He could not, they crucified him.

00:26:17.360 --> 00:26:22.200
