I think their genetics are little lower than normal,

00:31:32.400 --> 00:31:37.480
must be some animals in them otherwise how can they think

00:31:37.600 --> 00:31:42.280
that to be aggressive is being something higher.

00:31:42.400 --> 00:31:50.080
It's impossible, how can a person who is

00:31:50.200 --> 00:31:55.120
supposed to be a higher person, could be like a devil.

00:31:56.280 --> 00:31:59.360
How could Hitler say that he was a higher race

00:31:59.480 --> 00:32:02.120
when he was himself a devil?

00:32:02.240 --> 00:32:06.600
Is very nice for a devil to say I am a higher race.

00:32:08.600 --> 00:32:15.280
So in dealing in Sahaja Yoga, the sweetness of natural meekness

00:32:15.400 --> 00:32:20.960
not artificial of a businessman but a natural one

00:32:21.720 --> 00:32:31.040
that makes you shine with your great, great spirituality.

00:32:31.240 --> 00:32:35.640
Nobody can touch you, I have told you, except for you.

00:32:35.760 --> 00:32:40.160
You can only fall down but nobody can touch you,

00:32:40.280 --> 00:32:43.240
you are all protected from every angle.

00:32:43.360 --> 00:32:47.040
B ut if you want to hit yourself, I can't help it.

00:32:47.760 --> 00:32:50.240
So again we come to Tukarama saying,

00:32:50.360 --> 00:32:54.960
as Christ has said "know thyself ".

00:32:56.320 --> 00:33:02.120
First and foremost thing of introspection is: "Know thyself".

00:33:06.520 --> 00:33:08.280
What you are doing,

00:33:08.400 --> 00:33:12.120
are you trying to look at yourself or not?

00:33:12.240 --> 00:33:21.520
He has also said that we see a big beam into the eyes of others,

00:33:23.120 --> 00:33:27.240
then it's all right, but the beam is in your eyes

00:33:27.360 --> 00:33:32.360
and you start seeing the beam in others eyes and that's the point.

00:33:34.960 --> 00:33:38.120
So in your meditation you have to sit down

00:33:38.240 --> 00:33:41.720
and first of all introspect: "Oh Christ,

00:33:41.840 --> 00:33:46.280
Oh Sri Ganesha,  please give me wisdom to see myself

00:33:46.400 --> 00:33:53.160
and understand what's wrong with me, and understand

00:33:53.280 --> 00:34:00.760
where do I lack all the qualities of a good Sahaja Yogi.

00:34:02.480 --> 00:34:09.000
Just to meditate and you feel so happy, so joyous,

00:34:09.160 --> 00:34:13.240
because virtue within you gives you joy.

00:34:13.360 --> 00:34:16.760
But you don't say I'm virtuous, you don't say that,

00:34:16.880 --> 00:34:19.760
but the virtue within you, when you discover,

00:34:19.880 --> 00:34:21.440
that gives you joy

00:34:21.560 --> 00:34:28.640
and not your bad qualities and your hankerings,

00:34:28.760 --> 00:34:32.400
your lust and greed, no it does not.

00:34:33.840 --> 00:34:39.680
So we must really concentrate, even coming to Sahaja Yoga

00:34:39.800 --> 00:34:45.880
people think how I can use it for say fame?

00:34:46.080 --> 00:34:51.000
Leadership you see is another myth. Then they sometimes think

00:34:51.120 --> 00:34:54.920
why not use it for making some money some how.

00:34:55.960 --> 00:34:58.000
Some sort of a business they start.

00:34:58.120 --> 00:35:02.720
Don't do any business with Sahaja Yoga or Sahaja Yogis,

00:35:02.840 --> 00:35:06.600
I've told a hundred times, if you do it you'll be in trouble

00:35:06.720 --> 00:35:09.840
and then don't come and tell me the trouble.

00:35:10.560 --> 00:35:15.800
Sahaja Yoga is only God' s business, that's all.

00:35:18.840 --> 00:35:24.240
Everything that you are doing is for God and

00:35:24.360 --> 00:35:28.080
that's why you are doing it for your self.

00:35:28.600 --> 00:35:32.040
So introspection is very important,

00:35:32.160 --> 00:35:35.760
criticising others should be less and criticising yourself

00:35:35.880 --> 00:35:37.960
and laughing at yourself is the best.

00:35:38.080 --> 00:35:39.960
I laugh at myself many a times

00:35:40.080 --> 00:35:43.040
and say many things like that, if you have noticed,

00:35:43.160 --> 00:35:46.600
that makes life so interesting.

00:35:50.040 --> 00:35:53.080
That will kill your ego.

00:35:53.720 --> 00:35:56.680
How I am trying to assert myself

00:35:56.800 --> 00:36:00.960
and where is the meekness that Christ has talked about.

00:36:01.840 --> 00:36:05.640
It is a natural goodness within us.

00:36:05.960 --> 00:36:12.520
Once it shines and shows, you become so beautiful, so loveable.

00:36:12.640 --> 00:36:15.560
Whether you are sitting here near Me or there

00:36:15.680 --> 00:36:18.080
I know who is that kind.

00:36:18.200 --> 00:36:23.840
My heart just opens for such a personality.

00:36:24.120 --> 00:36:27.120
I know who they are.

00:36:32.520 --> 00:36:36.160
But even if I know I will never tell you,

00:36:36.280 --> 00:36:39.960
it is better that you know yourself.

00:36:40.080 --> 00:36:44.880
"Know thyself" is His  message,

00:36:44.960 --> 00:36:47.720
in the real way not with deception

00:36:47.840 --> 00:36:52.040
because you are deceiving yourself, whom are you deceiving,

00:36:52.160 --> 00:36:56.720
know thyself without any deception,

00:37:00.760 --> 00:37:06.880
without any lies, with full concentration.

00:37:07.880 --> 00:37:13.080
See where is your attention going, that's how you are going to rise,

00:37:13.200 --> 00:37:16.560
you are not going to rise by seeing the defects of others

00:37:16.680 --> 00:37:21.200
but you are going to rise only by seeing your own defects.

00:37:21.880 --> 00:37:24.400
Exactly this what Christ has said,

00:37:24.520 --> 00:37:28.520
I am telling you in very, very simple words.

00:37:29.840 --> 00:37:35.040
Then He has said love thy neighbour as thyself which is a very, very

00:37:35.160 --> 00:37:39.200
big thing to say. Now is only possible in Sahaja Yoga

00:37:39.320 --> 00:37:43.680
because you are collective, those who are not collective

00:37:43.800 --> 00:37:47.520
how can they love their neighbour. I mean who is the neighbour then,

00:37:47.640 --> 00:37:51.160
nobody's the neighbour, they're outsiders,

00:37:51.480 --> 00:37:53.920
but as soon as you become collective,

00:37:54.040 --> 00:37:57.720
see today there are fifty five nations, you are all so collective,

00:37:57.840 --> 00:38:01.240
so moral, so beautiful, no complications, nothing,

00:38:01.360 --> 00:38:03.880
I am so overjoyed to see that

00:38:03.960 --> 00:38:08.720
but to make it perfect we should introspect.

00:38:09.720 --> 00:38:13.200
Socially, collectively you people have improved a lot

00:38:13.320 --> 00:38:16.200
but also individually within yourself

00:38:16.320 --> 00:38:20.360
you have to improve for your own goodness.

00:38:22.400 --> 00:38:25.720
So on this great occasion, we have to celebrate

00:38:25.840 --> 00:38:31.240
because really such a great amount of work was done by Christ

00:38:31.360 --> 00:38:33.880
though neutralised by these horrible priests,

00:38:34.000 --> 00:38:37.800
which is done in every country, in every religion

00:38:37.920 --> 00:38:42.840
but now we should take a vow to save others

00:38:43.320 --> 00:38:46.280
who are taking the name of Christ and doing something

00:38:46.400 --> 00:38:51.680
just the opposite. If it could be done, if it could be achieved

00:38:51.800 --> 00:38:55.600
through your lives,  Christ's work has been done.

00:38:55.720 --> 00:39:01.680
You have to now express Christ through your life.

00:39:01.800 --> 00:39:04.240
This is what it is.

00:39:04.360 --> 00:39:09.320
Through your life you can express it, through the purity,

00:39:09.440 --> 00:39:13.160
through the meekness, through the compassion

00:39:13.280 --> 00:39:22.320
and the wisdom of Christ. Absolutely fearless was he

00:39:22.520 --> 00:39:25.000
and that's why you have to be fearless

00:39:25.120 --> 00:39:30.880
because you have to be only afraid of God and nobody else,

00:39:31.320 --> 00:39:34.560
that's all and if you have done nothing wrong then there's nothing

00:39:34.680 --> 00:39:38.320
to be afraid of God also because He loves you very much.

00:39:41.720 --> 00:39:48.840
So be clear cut about everything, be understanding,

00:39:49.880 --> 00:39:54.560
you are all loveable people no doubt but you should be such

00:39:54.680 --> 00:39:58.320
that you can adore yourself and love yourself

00:39:58.440 --> 00:40:00.840
because of the virtues you have.

00:40:01.280 --> 00:40:03.920
May God Bless you all.

